Experiment 2 Report
Depth Map to Point Cloud Generation using Deep Learning
1. Objective

The objective of Experiment 2 was to develop a deep learning model capable of converting monocular depth maps into 3D point clouds for pseudo-LiDAR generation using the KITTI dataset.

This stage extends the previous RGB-to-Depth experiment and attempts to reconstruct 3D spatial geometry from estimated depth information.

The overall research pipeline becomes:

RGB Image
    ↓
Depth Estimation Network
    ↓
Depth Map
    ↓
Point Cloud Prediction Network
    ↓
Pseudo LiDAR
